  "keyFeatures": [
    "Visual canvas for building creative workflows with drag-and-drop blocks",
    "AI-powered content generation using multiple models (Fal.ai, Gemini)",
    "Storyboard creation with scene and shot management",
    "Compute flow engine for connecting and executing generation pipelines",
    "Asset library with upload, generation, and management capabilities",
    "Real-time collaboration with Supabase",
    "Web3 integration with Thirdweb and ApeCoin",
    "Video editor integration for post-production"
